#~ "the document names and document urls are searched for matching text. "
#~ "While entering text in the search field you can use the cursor keys "
#~ "<keysym>Up</keysym> and <keysym>Down</keysym> to navigate in the list "
#~ "view. If the dialog is left with <guilabel>OK</guilabel> the plugin "
#~ "switches the view to the document selected in the list view. This makes "
